visible in the window behind the sculpture, with reflections of trees and nearby buildings in the glass." height="3024" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://cdn.some.pics/dhester/6a461f1f40b84.jpg" width="2268"/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Shared by &lt;a href="https://dhester.some.pics"&gt;@dhester&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 02 Jul 2026 08:19:51 +0000</pubDate></item><item><title/><link>https://some.pics/6a460bfabfa80</link><description>&lt;p&gt;#征稿启事：宗教、政治与认知战：信息、解读、阴谋与现实的斗争。www.jcrt.org/cw/&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="Conference flyer featuring the keynote speaker Jason Josephson and a brain/computer hybrid image." height="560" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://cdn.some.pics/adjb/6a460bfabfa80.webp" width="1180"/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Shared by &lt;a href="https://adjb.some.pics"&gt;@adjb&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 02 Jul 2026 06:58:05 +0000</pubDate></item></channel></rss>